OL,6,FA woman has been jailed for life after
OL,7,Fmurdering a man at his home in Kent.
OL,9,FNina Mercer lived at a flat in Newark
OL,10,FCourt, Gun Lane, Strood, with 61-year-
OL,11,Fold Alan Tomkins.
OL,13,FDuring the afternoon of 23 July 2024,
OL,14,FMr Tomkins was at home when Mercer
OL,15,Fstabbed him multiple times.
OL,17,FFollowing the attack, Mercer fled and
OL,18,Fmet a man she knew called Lee Robinson.
