OL,6,FPolice officers say the pair returned
OL,7,Fto the murder scene where Robinson
OL,8,Fstole Mr Tomkins' wallet and bank
OL,9,Fcard. He later used this to make
OL,10,Ffraudulent purchases.
OL,12,FMercer then travelled to Cuxton
OL,13,FLeisure Park in the victim's car where
OL,14,Fit is thought she got rid of her
OL,15,Fbloodstained clothing.
OL,17,FOn 25 July 2024, Kent Police officers
OL,18,Fwere contacted after an acquaintance
OL,19,Fof the victim raised concerns that he
OL,20,Fhad not been seen at work or at a
OL,21,Fplanned meeting.
