OL,3,CWoman jailed for life after murdering
OL,4,Cman at his home in Kent
OL,6,FOfficers went to his home and forced
OL,7,Ftheir way through the locked front
OL,8,Fdoor. They found Mr Tomkins laying
OL,9,Fdead in the hallway with a knife
OL,10,Fprotruding from his back. He had been
OL,11,Fstabbed six times.
OL,13,FWhile officers were at the scene,
OL,14,FMercer walked up to the property and
OL,15,Fshe was arrested.
OL,17,FRecovered CCTV footage showed Mercer's
OL,18,Fsuspicious movements near the victim's
OL,19,Fhome and traces of her DNA were found
OL,20,Fon the knife.
