OL,6,FMercer, 43, of Gun Lane, Strood, was
OL,7,Fconvicted of murder following a trial
OL,8,Fand will have to serve a minimum of 17
OL,9,Fyears before she is eligible for
OL,10,Fparole.
OL,12,FRobinson, 45, of Frindsbury Road,
OL,13,FStrood, was found not guilty of
OL,14,Fassisting an offender, but was
OL,15,Fconvicted of theft and fraud. He was
OL,16,Fjailed for two years and four months.
OL,18,FSenior investigating officer, DCI Emma
OL,19,FLawry, said: "The victim had allowed
OL,20,FNina Mercer to stay at his flat and is
OL,21,Fthought to have funded her lifestyle.
