OL,6,F"She callously repaid him in a brutal
OL,7,Fassault with a knife that ended his
OL,8,Flife.
OL,10,F"Mercer did not seek medical
OL,11,Fassistance for Mr Tomkins, but sought
OL,12,Fto cover her tracks. She denied her
OL,13,Fguilt, was convicted following a trial
OL,14,Fand has now been sentenced.
OL,16,F"I hope this now allows the victim's
OL,17,Frelatives and friends some closure
OL,18,Ffollowing these tragic events."
